This activates 'water + fire for grain', 'fire for vegetable', and 'fire for protein' bonuses for a perfect score. If you only use 'fire' on a three-ingredient mix without pre-soaking the grain, you'll get 80 points.

message: To achieve a score of 100, identify one vegetable, one protein, and one grain from your inventory. Use the 'stove' on the vegetable to get a 20-value cooked vegetable. Use the 'stove' on the protein to get a 20-value cooked protein. For the grain, first use 'water' on it, then use the 'stove' on the 'soaked grain' to get a 20-value cooked grain. Finally, combine these three valued items in two steps: first combine the cooked vegetable with the cooked grain (value 60), then combine this new item with the cooked protein (value 100). This order consistently yields the max score.
